# textdomain: mcl_clock
Clock=时钟
Displays the time of day in the Overworld=显示当前时间
Clocks are tools which shows the current time of day in the Overworld.=显示当前时间的工具。
The clock contains a rotating disc with a sun symbol (yellow disc) and moon symbol and a little “pointer” which shows the current time of day by estimating the real position of the sun and the moon in the sky. Noon is represented by the sun symbol and midnight is represented by the moon symbol.=包含一个带有太阳符号（黄色圆盘）和月亮符号的旋转圆盘，以及一枚小 "指针"。通过估算太阳和月亮在天空中的实际位置来显示当前时间。正午显示太阳符号，午夜显示月亮符号。
